This post is not only for the people that I’ve heavily been thankful this year but all the people that have helped me up until this point. Recently I’ve had some time to self reflect and I believe things most successful people are able to accomplish come from the people who play the back ground. So this post is for my endless amounts of “background people”. The people who bought a CD, the people who bought merch, the people who bought tickets for a show, the people who convinced me to keep going, the people who streamed a song, the people who commented (negative or positive things), the people who liked, the people who disliked, the people who shared, the people who didn’t share. I owe all of you a big thank you ! You made me stop looking at the specs I seen in others eyes and made me recognize the log I have in mine. Ima work in progress and I know with you guys I will always have a mirror to show me the Good and the Bad, and for that I Thank You!
.
.
.
.
#thankyougod 
#appreciationpost💕 
#thankyou 
#loveoverhate
